data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER. Catch this opportunity quickly! Property will be clear and vacant at closing. Being at 1750 square feet, this property is larger than others in the area. There is lots of opportunity for molding the property into your desired style! Move-in ready 3-bedroom, 1.5 bathroom, 1752 sf in this wonderful Greenville neighborhood. Step inside the front door to find an airy living room ready to be your entertainment headquarters. The kitchen offers plenty of cabinets and counter space. The large backyard is completely fenced. The shed provides additional storage for your backyard. This home will not disappoint.
